 Utility Classes Documentation
-------------------------------------
 This file contains reusable CSS classes 
 to simplify styling and avoid redundancy 
 in different projects.
=====================================
*/

/* 
=====================================
 1. Flex Center
-------------------------------------
 - A utility class for centering elements 
   both horizontally and vertically.
 - Useful for aligning content without 
   writing Flexbox code repeatedly.
 - Usage: <div class="flex-center"> Content </div>
=====================================
*/
.flex-center {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

/*
=====================================
 3. Button Styling
-------------------------------------
 - A modern button style with smooth hover effects.
 - The default background is white.
 - On hover, the background changes to a highlighted color.
=====================================
*/
.circle-btn {
  all: unset;
  background: white;
  color: black;
  border-radius: 50%;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.circle-btn:hover {
  background: #726d6d;
  color: white;
}